# Todo Tracking

`docs/todo.md` is the canonical MVP roadmap. After fully completing any item from this file, immediately update it by changing `- [ ]` to `- [x]` for that item.

- Update only items that are **fully and verifiably done** — not partially complete ones.
- If a phase is fully completed, tick all its items in one edit.
- Never tick items the user hasn't confirmed (e.g. IntelliJ setup, manual verification steps).
